item.title: Gallery Salamanca Arts and Crafts Hobart Tasmania
item.description:
Gallery Salamanca Arts and Crafts Hobart Tasmania

A celebration of the arts, Gallery Salamanca's mission is to support and serve artists and craftspeople by engaging the community through the sale of arts and crafts and the promotion of exhibits. Our purpose is to support, preserve and commemorate Australian, specifically Tasmanian, handmade works and their makers.
